{"tid":301261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佔領金紫荊廣場團體訴求：無條件釋放劉曉波 香港市民要真普選","createTime":"2017-06-28T13:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T14:07:50.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"95c4a42215b6985be9f0f605bb5b2afdcf7076af","tid":301261,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T13:19:42.000Z","msg":"【直播】佔領金紫荊清場！警拘30人涉妨礙公眾使用雕像<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170628/large/1498654078_1f9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170628%2Flarge%2F1498654078_1f9d.jpg&h=4ffa7662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示威者留守黑紫荊宣言全文<br />\n<br />\n前天晨光來到，我們用黑布網罩金紫荊雕像，銅雕沒有搖動，它的虛偽卻不可再閃耀。謊言被撕破，我們方可在凋謝中掙扎與重生。今夜，我們在習近平訪港前夕，將再次遮蓋雕像虛妄的金光，並堅決留守，在黑紫荊廣場等待新的晨光。我們呼籲香港人來援，前往廣場一同留守！<br />\n<br />\n主權移交二十年來，香港市民受盡欺壓，貧無立錐 : 不僅是經濟民生上的貧困，更是政治權利上的貧弱。在中國大陸，追求民主自由者如劉曉波，更是歷盡磨難，中共竟以十年牢獄，間接殺死一名諾貝爾和平獎得主，實在無法無天。在中共專權之下，莫不是悲苦的自由靈魂。<br />\n<br />\n為此我們必須再次走在抗爭的路上，與當權者二十年來的不公不義對抗。絕不讓習近平及其權貴爪牙，粉飾太平，在香港的土地上，慶祝中港人民的苦難！<br />\n<br />\n讓我們在黑紫荊廣場集結！撤回人大八三一決定！落實真正普選！立即釋放劉曉波！<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志、社民連、人民力量、大專政關<br />\n2017年6月28日<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170628/56887961\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170628%2F56887961&d=eyh8dWm41L%2BHSmBjO9KuD7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=8024bfa1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170628%2F56887961&h=aef7ecb4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170628/56887961</a>"},{"pid":"3c62391833aa5f63066a91fe0086ccfbe793f0b2","tid":301261,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T13:22:11.000Z","msg":"回帶<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/11659332_10153409202299929_1712077641047252904_n-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2F11659332_10153409202299929_1712077641047252904_n-1.jpg&h=81c66750&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a94d5e3cb4bd070701ce7bf4cdbc210e62477d95","tid":301261,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T13:23:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a30e1c2c10a053f5e4dae71cfd5416b3964c0a6a","tid":301261,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T13:26:54.000Z","msg":"講來講去 咪又係：<br />\n支持民主回歸<br />\n建設民主中國"},{"pid":"b7dcb94f5f2df0af4c499e04ab686080d2f8e8d5","tid":301261,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T13:27:31.000Z","msg":"突發"},{"pid":"e8d00381e648fc131e576399b15f936650429cdc","tid":301261,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T13:50:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f8237521032cee512480c43ae9cad6a78bc0acb","tid":301261,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:04:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85444f553726c1d52d4c64bfc20a02a67e251902","tid":301261,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:07:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}